awards.text: Nominated for 1 Oscar. Another 9 wins & 3 nominations.

fullplot: The Other Side of Sunday, Also known in Norwegian as "Sndags Engler", is a movie that criticizes the small, and often tight church community. We follow the Preachers Daughter; Maria in her journey to liberate herself from the stiff church community and her father.
